#TITLE: THE DUCK GAME

#SETTINGS: The duck goes out to the PARK to enjoy some time and relax. At the PARK, there is a PLAYGROUND that has a SWING, SANDBOX, and TREE. But another location seems to catch the duck's eye. The LEMONADE STAND.

#SUMMARY: The duck wants some grapes but he has no supermarket that is near.. He soon goes to the park to have a nice relaxing time but something about the lemonade stand seems off.. Play and find out.

#LISTS OF VARIABLES:
    #haveDrank: If you drank the lemonade at the lemonade stand
    #haveSwung: if you have swung on the swing at the playground that kicks you to another day
    #haveHammer: If you have acquired the hammer to destroy the lemonade stand
    #haveMoney: If you have money to pay for the lemonade
    #day: the amount of days you have completed
    #visitLemon: how many times you visited the lemonade stand


